headline: The Merger Between Kimberly-Clark And Kenvue Clearly Favors One Party
summary: Kenvue and Kimberly-Clark are merging in a $32B deal with $2.1B in synergies and major consumer health potential. Learn why KVUE and KMB are rated hold.
